 2018-12752018-10-10,  ,  FIN,  , 
ActCanadian International Trade Tribunal Act
SubjectOrder Referring to the Canadian International Trade Tribunal
PrecisOrder Referring to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL, for Inquiry into and Reporting on, the Matter of the Importation of Certain Steel Goods into Canada, to determine whether the Canadian producers of such steel goods are injured by increased imports, and if so, whether final safeguard measures are warranted to address it (after the expiry of the 200-day provisional safeguard measures).
